import React from 'react';
import {
    IonMenu,
    IonHeader,
    IonToolbar,
    IonTitle,
    IonContent,
    IonList,
    IonItem,
    IonRouterOutlet,
    IonMenuToggle
} from '@ionic/react';

export const Menu: React.FC = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <IonMenu contentId="main" menuId="main-menu">
                <IonHeader>
                    <IonToolbar color="primary">
                        <IonTitle>Start Menu</IonTitle>
                    </IonToolbar>
                </IonHeader>
                <IonContent>
                    <IonMenuToggle>
                        <IonItem>Home</IonItem>
                    </IonMenuToggle>
                    <IonMenuToggle>
                        <IonItem>About</IonItem>
                    </IonMenuToggle>
                </IonContent>
            </IonMenu>
            <IonRouterOutlet id="main"></IonRouterOutlet>
        </>
    );
}
